1701	//
1702	// Drives the Dockerfile FROM-line hygiene contract through the rbw-fhc and
1703	// rbw-fhv tabtargets — exercising the contract surface, not module internals.
1704	// Eight synthetic cases (5 positive, 3 negative) feed inline Dockerfile bodies
1705	// to rbw-fhc; one all-vessels case iterates real conjure vessels through
1706	// rbw-fhv with a Rust-side counter that fails verdict on zero iterations.
